												<div class="vers-no">6</div>
						<div class="vers-content">There is a proverb; a boy will keep the course he has begun; even when he grows old, he will not leave it.<a href="" class="inline-comment" data-comment-id="1057">âœ»</a> <span class="content-paragraph"><br><br></span></div>
					</div>
