												<div class="vers-no">8</div>
						<div class="vers-content">Who sows mischief, reaps a sorry crop; ere long, the flail of his malice will have done its work.<a href="" class="inline-comment" data-comment-id="1058">âœ»</a></div>
					</div>
									<div id="vers162231" class="vers">
												<div class="vers-no">9</div>
						<div class="vers-content">For every loaf of bread given to the hungry, blessing shall be the reward of kindly hearts. (A renowned victory he wins, that is a bestower of gifts, and living men are the spoils of it.<a href="" class="inline-comment" data-comment-id="1059">âœ»</a> )<span class="content-paragraph"><br><br></span></div>
