												<div class="vers-no">12</div>
						<div class="vers-content">True knowledge has the Lordâ€™s smile for its protection; the schemerâ€™s cause he will overthrow.<span class="content-paragraph"><br><br></span></div>
					</div>
									<div id="vers162235" class="vers">
												<div class="vers-no">13</div>
						<div class="vers-content">Out? says Sloth; why, there is a lion without; wouldst thou have me slain in the open street?<span class="content-paragraph"><br><br></span></div>
					</div>
