												<div class="vers-no">15</div>
						<div class="vers-content">Boyhoodâ€™s mind is loaded with a pack of folly, that needs the rod of correction to shift it.<span class="content-paragraph"><br><br></span></div>
					</div>
									<div id="vers162238" class="vers">
												<div class="vers-no">16</div>
						<div class="vers-content">Oppress the poor for thy enrichment, and ere long a richer manâ€™s claim shall impoverish thee.<a href="" class="inline-comment" data-comment-id="1060">âœ»</a> <span class="content-paragraph"><br><br></span></div>
					</div>
									<div id="vers162239" class="vers">
